<eesti>Kaabelleviseadus </eesti>
<inglise>Cable Distribution Act </inglise>
<eesti>Vastu v&otilde;etud 31. mail 2001. a. </eesti>
<inglise>Passed 31 May 2001 </inglise>
<eesti>(RT I 2001, 53, 310), </eesti>
<inglise>(RT (1) I 2001, 53, 310), </inglise>
<eesti>j&otilde;ustunud 20. juulil 2001. a. </eesti>
<inglise>entered into force 20 July 2001. </inglise>
<eesti>1. peat&uuml;kk </eesti>
<inglise>Chapter 1 </inglise>
<eesti>&Uuml;lds&auml;tted </eesti>
<inglise>General Provisions </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 1. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 1. </inglise>
<eesti>Seaduse &uuml;lesanne </eesti>
<inglise>Purpose of Act </inglise>
<eesti>K&auml;esoleva seaduse &uuml;lesanne on luua tingimused kaabelleviteenuse osutamiseks ja tarbija kaitseks. </eesti>
<inglise>The purpose of this Act is to create conditions for the provision of cable distribution services and for the protection of consumer rights. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 2. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 2. </inglise>
<eesti>Kaabelleviteenus </eesti>
<inglise>Cable distribution services </inglise>
<eesti>Kaabelleviteenus k&auml;esoleva seaduse t&auml;henduses on televisiooni- v&otilde;i raadiosaadete ja televisiooni- v&otilde;i raadioprogrammide (edaspidi programmid) tasuline v&otilde;i tasuta edastamine tarbijale kaabelleviv&otilde;rgu v&otilde;i &uuml;hisantennis&uuml;steemi kaudu. </eesti>
<inglise>For the purposes of this Act, cable distribution services is the transmission of television or radio broadcasts and television or radio programmes (hereinafter programmes) to consumers for a charge or without charge through cable networks or by master antenna systems. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 3. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 3. </inglise>
<eesti>Kaabelleviv&otilde;rk </eesti>
<inglise>Cable network </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Kaabelleviv&otilde;rk k&auml;esoleva seaduse t&auml;henduses on territoriaalselt piiritletud tehniliste vahendite kogum, mille kaudu v&otilde;etakse vastu ja edastatakse tarbijale programme, mis on: </eesti>
<inglise>(1) For the purposes of this Act, cable network is a set of technical facilities within a defined territory through which programmes are received and transmitted to consumers, and such programmes are: </inglise>
<eesti>1) v&auml;ljastatud maapealsete ringh&auml;&auml;lingusaatjate abil; </eesti>
<inglise>1) emitted by terrestrial broadcasting transmitters; </inglise>
<eesti>2) v&auml;ljastatud satelliitide abil v&otilde;i </eesti>
<inglise>2) emitted by satellites; or </inglise>
<eesti>3) antud edastamiseks ringh&auml;&auml;linguorganisatsioonide poolt. </eesti>
<inglise>3) to be transmitted on authorisation of broadcasters. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Kaabelleviv&otilde;rgu kaudu telekommunikatsiooniteenuse osutamisel peab ettev&otilde;tja t&auml;itma telekommunikatsiooniseaduses (RT I 2000, 18, 116; 78, 495; 2001, 23, 125) s&auml;testatud n&otilde;udeid. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) In the provision of telecommunication services by cable network, undertakings shall comply with the requirements provided for in the Telecommunication Act (RT I 2000, 18, 116; 78, 495; 2001, 23, 125). </inglise>
<eesti>(3) Kaabelleviv&otilde;rgu kasutamine ei v&otilde;i kahjustada programmide vastuv&otilde;tmist v&otilde;i edastamist teiste &otilde;iguslikul alusel rajatud kaabelleviv&otilde;rkude, &uuml;hisantennis&uuml;steemide v&otilde;i individuaalvastuv&otilde;tus&uuml;steemide kaudu ega tekitada raadioh&auml;ireid. </eesti>
<inglise>(3) The use of a cable network shall not interfere with the reception or transmission of programmes through other cable networks, by master antenna systems or individual reception systems constructed on a legal basis, or create radio interference. </inglise>
<eesti>(4) Kaabelleviv&otilde;rgule esitatavad tehnilised n&otilde;uded kehtestab teede- ja sideminister, l&auml;htudes j&auml;rgmistest p&otilde;him&otilde;tetest: </eesti>
<inglise>(4) The Minister of Transport and Communications shall establish the technical requirements for cable networks on the basis of the following principles: </inglise>
<eesti>1) toimimise turvalisuse tagamine; </eesti>
<inglise>1) ensurance of the security of operations; </inglise>
<eesti>2) terviklikkuse s&auml;ilitamine; </eesti>
<inglise>2) preservation of integrity; </inglise>
<eesti>3) tervise- ja keskkonnan&otilde;uete j&auml;rgimine; </eesti>
<inglise>3) compliance with health and environmental requirements; </inglise>
<eesti>4) planeeringu ja maakorraldusn&otilde;uete j&auml;rgimine; </eesti>
<inglise>4) compliance with planning and land readjustment requirements; </inglise>
<eesti>5) raadiov&otilde;rkude ning maailmaruumis v&otilde;i Maal asuvate muude tehniliste s&uuml;steemide vahel kahjulike ja h&auml;irivate m&otilde;jutuste v&auml;ltimine; </eesti>
<inglise>5) avoidance of harmful interference between radio networks and other outer space based or terrestrial technical systems; </inglise>
<eesti>6) avaliku korra ja riikliku julgeoleku tagamine; </eesti>
<inglise>6) ensurance of public order and national security; </inglise>
<eesti>7) kehtivate n&otilde;uete j&auml;rgimise kontrollimine; </eesti>
<inglise>7) monitoring of compliance with the established requirements; </inglise>
<eesti>8) vaba konkurentsi kahjustava tegevuse v&auml;ltimine. </eesti>
<inglise>8) avoidance of activities which prejudice free competition. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 4. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 4. </inglise>
<eesti>&Uuml;hisantennis&uuml;steem </eesti>
<inglise>Master antenna system </inglise>
<eesti>(1) &Uuml;hisantennis&uuml;steem k&auml;esoleva seaduse t&auml;henduses on tehniliste vahendite kogum, mille abil v&otilde;etakse vastu ja edastatakse ainult &uuml;he kinnisasja, ehitise v&otilde;i &uuml;histu piires asuvatele tarbijatele programme, mis on v&auml;ljastatud: </eesti>
<inglise>(1) For the purposes of this Act, master antenna system is a set of technical facilities through which programmes are received and transmitted to consumers located within the limits of one immovable, building or association, and such programmes are emitted by: </inglise>
<eesti>1) maapealsete ringh&auml;&auml;lingusaatjate abil v&otilde;i </eesti>
<inglise>1) terrestrial broadcasting transmitters; or </inglise>
<eesti>2) satelliitide abil. </eesti>
<inglise>2) satellite. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) &Uuml;hisantennis&uuml;steemi kasutamine ei v&otilde;i kahjustada programmide vastuv&otilde;tmist v&otilde;i edastamist teiste &otilde;iguslikul alusel rajatud kaabelleviv&otilde;rkude, &uuml;hisantennis&uuml;steemide v&otilde;i individuaalvastuv&otilde;tus&uuml;steemide kaudu ega tekitada raadioh&auml;ireid. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) The use of a master antenna system shall not interfere with the reception or transmission of programmes through other cable networks, by master antenna systems or individual reception systems constructed on a legal basis, or create radio interference. </inglise>
<eesti>(3) &Uuml;hisantennis&uuml;steemile esitatavad tehnilised n&otilde;uded kehtestab teede- ja sideminister, l&auml;htudes k&auml;esoleva seaduse &sect; 3 l&otilde;ikes 4 s&auml;testatud p&otilde;him&otilde;tetest. </eesti>
<inglise>(3) The Minister of Transport and Communications shall establish the technical requirements for master antenna systems on the basis of the principles provided for in subsection 3 (4) of this Act. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 5. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 5. </inglise>
<eesti>Individuaalvastuv&otilde;tus&uuml;steem </eesti>
<inglise>Individual reception system </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Individuaalvastuv&otilde;tus&uuml;steem k&auml;esoleva seaduse t&auml;henduses on tehniliste vahendite kogum, mille abil isik v&otilde;i isikud &uuml;hiselt v&otilde;tavad ainult &uuml;he kinnisasja v&otilde;i ehitise piires oma tarbeks vastu programme, mis on v&auml;ljastatud: </eesti>
<inglise>(1) For the purposes of this Act, individual reception system is a set of technical facilities whereby a person receives or several persons jointly receive programmes for their own use within the limits of one immovable, building or association, and such programmes are emitted by: </inglise>
<eesti>1) maapealsete ringh&auml;&auml;lingusaatjate abil v&otilde;i </eesti>
<inglise>1) terrestrial broadcasting transmitters; or </inglise>
<eesti>2) satelliitide abil. </eesti>
<inglise>2) satellite. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Individuaalvastuv&otilde;tus&uuml;steemi kaudu programmide edastamine teisele isikule ei ole lubatud. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) The transmission of programmes to other persons by individual reception systems is not permitted. </inglise>
<eesti>(3) Individuaalvastuv&otilde;tus&uuml;steemi kasutamine ei v&otilde;i kahjustada programmide vastuv&otilde;tmist v&otilde;i edastamist teiste &otilde;iguslikul alusel rajatud kaabelleviv&otilde;rkude, &uuml;hisantennis&uuml;steemide v&otilde;i individuaalvastuv&otilde;tus&uuml;steemide kaudu ega tekitada raadioh&auml;ireid. </eesti>
<inglise>(3) The use of an individual reception system shall not interfere with the reception or transmission of programmes through cable networks, by master antenna systems or individual reception systems constructed on a legal basis, or create radio interference. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 6. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 6. </inglise>
<eesti>Tarbija </eesti>
<inglise>Consumer </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Tarbija k&auml;esoleva seaduse t&auml;henduses on isik, kes on liitunud kaabelleviv&otilde;rgu v&otilde;i &uuml;hisantennis&uuml;steemiga ja kellel on kaabelleviv&otilde;rguloa omaniku, &uuml;hisantennis&uuml;steemi omaniku v&otilde;i kaabelleviteenuse osutajaga s&otilde;lmitud liitumisleping v&otilde;i teenuse osutamise leping. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) For the purposes of this Act, consumer is a person who has subscribed to a cable network or master antenna system and who has entered into a subscription contract or contract for provision of services with the holder of a cable network licence, owner of an individual reception system or provider of cable distribution services. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Tarbijal ei ole &otilde;igust edastada programme teisele isikule. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) Consumers have no right to transmit programmes to other persons. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 7. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 7. </inglise>
<eesti>Kaabelleviv&otilde;rgu v&otilde;i &uuml;hisantennis&uuml;steemi omanik </eesti>
<inglise>Owner or cable network or individual reception system </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Kaabelleviv&otilde;rgu omanikuks v&otilde;ib olla &auml;riregistrisse kantud ettev&otilde;tja v&otilde;i seaduse alusel teise registrisse kantud juriidiline isik, kellele on k&auml;esoleva seaduse alusel v&auml;ljastatud kaabelleviv&otilde;rguluba. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) An undertaking entered in the commercial register or a legal person entered in another register pursuant to law, which has been issued a cable network licence pursuant to this Act may be the owner of a cable network. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Kaabelleviv&otilde;rgu omanik ei tohi olla Eestis telekommunikatsiooniv&otilde;rgu baasil osutatava telefoniteenuse k&auml;ibest rohkem kui 40 protsenti omav ettev&otilde;tja v&otilde;i sellises &auml;ri&uuml;hingus vahetult v&otilde;i osanike, aktsion&auml;ride v&otilde;i kolmandate isikute kaudu &uuml;le 10 protsendi suurust osalust omav ettev&otilde;tja. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) The owner of a cable network shall not be an undertaking which accounts for more than 40 per cent of the turnover in the market of telephone services which are provided in Estonia or an undertaking which has a holding of more than 10 per cent in such company either directly or through partners, shareholders or third persons. </inglise>
<eesti>(3) &Uuml;hisantennis&uuml;steemi omanikuks v&otilde;ib olla f&uuml;&uuml;silisest isikust ettev&otilde;tja v&otilde;i juriidiline isik, kes on seaduses s&auml;testatud n&otilde;uetele vastavalt registreeritud. </eesti>
<inglise>(3) A sole proprietor or a legal person who has been registered in compliance with the requirements provided for in the law may be the owner of a master antenna system. </inglise>
<eesti>(4) Kaabelleviv&otilde;rgu v&otilde;i &uuml;hisantennis&uuml;steemi omanik korraldab ja vastutab kaabelleviv&otilde;rgu v&otilde;i &uuml;hisantennis&uuml;steemi loomise, arendamise ja kasutamise eest. </eesti>
<inglise>(4) The owner of a cable network or a master antenna system organises and is responsible for the creation, development and use of the cable network or master antenna system. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 8. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 8. </inglise>
<eesti>Kaabelleviteenuse osutaja </eesti>
<inglise>Provider of cable distribution services </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Kaabelleviteenuse osutaja on ettev&otilde;tja, kes edastab kaabellevi- v&otilde;i telekommunikatsiooniv&otilde;rgu v&otilde;i &uuml;hisantennis&uuml;steemi kaudu tarbijale programme. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) A provider of cable distribution services is an undertaking which transmits programs to consumers through cable or telecommunications network or by master antenna system. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Kaabelleviteenuse osutajaks v&otilde;ib olla kaabelleviv&otilde;rgu omanik v&otilde;i kaabelleviv&otilde;rguloa omanikuga vastava lepingu s&otilde;lminud ettev&otilde;tja. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) The owner of a cable network or an undertaking which has entered into a corresponding contract with a holder of a cable network licence may act as a provider of cable distribution services. </inglise>
<eesti>(3) Kaabelleviteenuse osutajaks ei tohi olla Eestis telekommunikatsiooniv&otilde;rgu baasil osutatava telefoniteenuse k&auml;ibest rohkem kui 40 protsenti omav ettev&otilde;tja v&otilde;i sellises &auml;ri&uuml;hingus vahetult v&otilde;i osanike, aktsion&auml;ride v&otilde;i kolmandate isikute kaudu &uuml;le 10 protsendi suurust osalust omav ettev&otilde;tja. </eesti>
<inglise>(3) A provider of cable distribution services shall not be an undertaking which accounts for more than 40 per cent of the turnover in the market of telephone services which are provided in Estonia or an undertaking which has a holding of more than 10 per cent in such company either directly or through partners, shareholders or third persons. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 9. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 9. </inglise>
<eesti>Kaabellevi programmide pakett ja p&otilde;hipakett </eesti>
<inglise>Package of programmes distributed by cable and basic package of programmes distributed by cable </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Kaabellevi programmide pakett on kaabelleviv&otilde;rgu kaudu tarbijale edastatavate programmide kogum. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) Package of programmes distributed by cable is a collection of programmes transmitted to consumers through a cable network. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Kaabellevi programmide p&otilde;hipakett on kaabellevi programmide pakett, mida kaabelleviv&otilde;rgu omanik peab edastama temaga liitumislepingu s&otilde;lminud tarbijale. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) Basic package of programmes distributed by cable is a package of programmes distributed by cable which the owner of a cable network must transmit to consumers who have entered into a subscription contract with the owner. </inglise>
<eesti>(3) Kaabellevi programmide p&otilde;hipaketti mittekuuluvate programmide edastamiseks s&otilde;lmitakse tarbijaga eraldi teenuse osutamise leping v&otilde;i liitumislepingu lisa. </eesti>
<inglise>(3) In order to transmit programmes which are not included in the basic package of programmes, a separate contract for provision of services shall be entered into with a consumer or an annex to the subscription contract is signed. </inglise>
<eesti>2. peat&uuml;kk </eesti>
<inglise>Chapter 2 </inglise>
<eesti>Kaabelleviv&otilde;rguluba </eesti>
<inglise>Cable Network Licence </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 10. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 10. </inglise>
<eesti>Kaabelleviv&otilde;rguluba </eesti>
<inglise>Cable network licence </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Kaabelleviv&otilde;rguluba on Sideameti poolt v&auml;ljastatud tegevusluba, mis annab sellel m&auml;rgitud isikule &otilde;iguse kaabelleviv&otilde;rgu loomiseks, arendamiseks ja kasutamiseks loaga m&auml;&auml;ratud tingimustel. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) Cable network licence is an activity licence issued by the Communications Board which entitles the person indicated therein to create, develop and use a cable network under the conditions specified in the licence. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Kaabelleviv&otilde;rguluba v&auml;ljastatakse t&auml;htajaga 10 aastat, kui selle loa taotleja ei soovi l&uuml;hemat t&auml;htaega. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) A cable network licence is issued for a term of ten years unless the applicant requests a shorter term. </inglise>
<eesti>(3) Kaabelleviv&otilde;rguluba ei ole &uuml;leantav. </eesti>
<inglise>(3) A cable network licence is not transferable. </inglise>
<eesti>(4) Kui kaabelleviv&otilde;rk v&otilde;i selle osa v&otilde;&otilde;randatakse teisele isikule ja kui uus omanik esitab Sideametile kahe n&auml;dala jooksul, arvates omandi &uuml;leminekust, kaabelleviv&otilde;rguloa taotluse, kehtivad eelmisele omanikule v&auml;ljastatud kaabelleviv&otilde;rguloast tulenevad &otilde;igused ja kohustused uue omaniku suhtes kuni taotluse l&auml;bivaatamiseni Sideameti poolt. </eesti>
<inglise>(4) If a cable network or a part thereof is transferred to a third person and the new owner submits an application for a cable network licence to the Communications Board within two weeks as of the transfer of the ownership, the rights and obligations arising from the cable network licence issued to the former owner remain valid with regard to the new owner until the application of the new owner is reviewed by the Communications Board. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 11. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 11. </inglise>
<eesti>Kaabelleviv&otilde;rguloaga m&auml;&auml;ratavad tingimused </eesti>
<inglise>Conditions specified by cable network licence </inglise>
<eesti>Kaabelleviv&otilde;rguloaga m&auml;&auml;ratakse kindlaks: </eesti>
<inglise>A cable network licence shall specify: </inglise>
<eesti>1) tegevuse geograafiline piirkond; </eesti>
<inglise>1) the geographical area of the activity; </inglise>
<eesti>2) kaabelleviv&otilde;rgule esitatavad tehnilised n&otilde;uded; </eesti>
<inglise>2) technical requirements for cable network; </inglise>
<eesti>3) tegevuse alustamise aeg; </eesti>
<inglise>3) commencement date of activity; </inglise>
<eesti>4) muud k&auml;esoleva seadusega s&auml;testatud n&otilde;uded. </eesti>
<inglise>4) other requirements provided by this Act. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 12. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 12. </inglise>
<eesti>Kaabelleviv&otilde;rguloa taotlemine </eesti>
<inglise>Application for cable network licence </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Kaabelleviv&otilde;rku luua, arendada ja kasutada sooviv isik esitab Sideametile vormikohase taotluse kaabelleviv&otilde;rguloa v&auml;ljastamiseks. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) A person who wishes to create, develop and use a cable network shall submit a standard format application for the issue of a cable network licence to the Communications Board. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Kaabelleviv&otilde;rguloa v&auml;ljastamise taotlus peab sisaldama taotleja kohta j&auml;rgmisi andmeid: </eesti>
<inglise>(2) The application for a cable network licence shall contain the following information concerning the applicant: </inglise>
<eesti>1) nimi ja registrikood; </eesti>
<inglise>1) name and registry code; </inglise>
<eesti>2) aadress ja muud kontaktandmed; </eesti>
<inglise>2) address and other details; </inglise>
<eesti>3) tegevuse alustamise aeg; </eesti>
<inglise>3) commencement date of activity; </inglise>
<eesti>4) tegevuse geograafiline piirkond. </eesti>
<inglise>4) geographical area of activity. </inglise>
<eesti>(3) Kaabelleviv&otilde;rguloa taotlusele tuleb lisada: </eesti>
<inglise>(3) The following shall be appended to an application for a cable network licence: </inglise>
<eesti>1) kaabelleviv&otilde;rgu ja osutatava kaabelleviteenuse kirjeldus; </eesti>
<inglise>1) description of the cable network and the cable distribution service provided; </inglise>
<eesti>2) juriidilisel isikul v&otilde;i f&uuml;&uuml;silisest isikust ettev&otilde;tjal t&otilde;estatud v&auml;ljav&otilde;te registrist, kus isik on registreeritud, v&otilde;i juriidilise isiku asutamisel s&otilde;lmitud asutamislepingu t&otilde;estatud &auml;rakiri; </eesti>
<inglise>2) in case of a legal person or a sole proprietor, a certified extract of the register in which the person is registered, or a certified copy of the memorandum of association of a legal person; </inglise>
<eesti>3) juriidilisel isikul aktsion&auml;ride v&otilde;i osanike nimekiri, kellel on v&auml;hemalt 10-protsendiline osalus aktsia- v&otilde;i osakapitalis; </eesti>
<inglise>3) in case of a legal person, the list of shareholders or partners who have at least a 10 per cent holding in the share capital; </inglise>
<eesti>4) riigil&otilde;ivu tasumist t&otilde;endav dokument. </eesti>
<inglise>4) a document certifying the payment of state fees. </inglise>
<eesti>(4) Kaabelleviv&otilde;rguloa ja taotluse vormid kehtestab teede- ja sideminister. </eesti>
<inglise>(4) The format of the cable network licences and application shall be established by the Minister of Transport and Communications. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 13. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 13. </inglise>
<eesti>Kaabelleviv&otilde;rguloa v&auml;ljastamine </eesti>
<inglise>Issue of cable network licence </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Sideamet v&auml;ljastab kaabelleviv&otilde;rguloa koos kaabelleviv&otilde;rgule esitatavate n&otilde;uetega. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) The Communications Board shall issue a cable network licence together with requirements for the cable network. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Kaabelleviv&otilde;rguluba v&auml;ljastatakse hiljemalt kaheksa n&auml;dala jooksul, arvates n&otilde;uetekohase taotluse ja k&otilde;igi n&otilde;utavate dokumentide laekumisest Sideametile. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) A cable network licence shall be issued not later than within eight weeks after the receipt of a correctly completed application and all required documents at the Communications Board. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 14. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 14. </inglise>
<eesti>Kaabelleviv&otilde;rguloa v&auml;ljastamisest keeldumine </eesti>
<inglise>Refusal to issue cable network licence </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Sideamet keeldub kaabelleviv&otilde;rguloa v&auml;ljastamisest, kui: </eesti>
<inglise>(1) The Communications Board shall refuse to issue a cable network licence, if: </inglise>
<eesti>1) taotluse esitaja ei suuda tagada k&auml;esoleva seaduse alusel kehtestatud n&otilde;uete t&auml;itmist; </eesti>
<inglise>1) the applicant is unable to ensure compliance with the requirements established pursuant to this Act; </inglise>
<eesti>2) esitatud taotlus ei vasta seaduses s&auml;testatud n&otilde;uetele v&otilde;i </eesti>
<inglise>2) the application does not conform to the requirements established by law, or </inglise>
<eesti>3) taotluses v&otilde;i sellele lisatuna on esitatud eba&otilde;igeid v&otilde;i ebat&auml;pseid andmeid. </eesti>
<inglise>3) the information submitted in the application or annexed thereto is incorrect or inaccurate. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Sideamet v&otilde;ib anda taotluse esitajale t&auml;htaja kaabelleviv&otilde;rguloa v&auml;ljastamist takistavate asjaolude k&otilde;rvaldamiseks. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) The Communications Board may grant a term to an applicant for the elimination of the circumstances which impede the issue of a cable network licence. </inglise>
<eesti>T&auml;htaja andmisest teatab Sideamet kirjalikult taotluse esitajale, m&auml;rkides t&auml;htaja andmise aluse ja aja, mille jooksul tuleb puudused k&otilde;rvaldada. </eesti>
<inglise>The Communications Board shall notify the applicant in writing of the grant of a term and shall indicate the basis for granting the term and the period during which deficiencies must be eliminated. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 15. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 15. </inglise>
<eesti>Kaabelleviv&otilde;rguloa kehtivuse pikendamine </eesti>
<inglise>Extension of cable network licence </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Kaabelleviv&otilde;rguloa kehtivuse pikendamiseks esitab kaabelleviv&otilde;rgu omanik hiljemalt kolm kuud enne loa kehtivust&auml;htaja l&otilde;ppemist vabas vormis kirjaliku taotluse kaabelleviv&otilde;rguloa t&auml;htaja pikendamiseks koos riigil&otilde;ivu tasumist t&otilde;endava dokumendiga. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) For the extension of a cable network licence, the owner of a cable network shall, not later than three months before the expiry of the validity of the licence, submit a written application prepared in a free format for the extension of the cable network licence and the document certifying the payment of the state fee. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Kaabelleviv&otilde;rguloa kehtivuse pikendab Sideamet &uuml;he kuu jooksul, arvates k&auml;esoleva paragrahvi l&otilde;ikes 1 nimetatud dokumentide laekumisest. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) The Communications Board shall extend a cable network licence within one month after the date of receipt of the documents specified in subsection (1) of this section. </inglise>
<eesti>(3) Kaabelleviv&otilde;rguloa kehtivuse pikendamisel j&auml;&auml;vad kehtima k&otilde;ik kaabelleviv&otilde;rguloaga m&auml;&auml;ratud tingimused. </eesti>
<inglise>(3) Upon the extension of a cable network licence, all conditions specified in the licence remain valid. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 16. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 16. </inglise>
<eesti>Kaabelleviv&otilde;rguloa tingimuste muutmine </eesti>
<inglise>Amendment of conditions of cable network licence </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Sideamet v&otilde;ib muuta kaabelleviv&otilde;rguloa tingimusi, kui muudatustega ei rikuta v&otilde;rdse kohtlemise ja vaba konkurentsi p&otilde;him&otilde;tteid ning kui muutmine on p&otilde;hjustatud: </eesti>
<inglise>(1) The Communications Board may amend the conditions of a cable network licence if such amendments do not result in violation of the principles of equal treatment and free competition and are due to: </inglise>
<eesti>1) kaabelleviv&otilde;rguloa vastavusse viimisest teiste &otilde;igusaktidega v&otilde;i </eesti>
<inglise>1) bringing the cable network licence into compliance with the provisions of other legislation, or </inglise>
<eesti>2) tehnoloogia arengust. </eesti>
<inglise>2) technology development. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Sideamet teavitab kirjalikult kaabelleviv&otilde;rguloa omanikku k&auml;esoleva paragrahvi l&otilde;ike 1 alusel kaabelleviv&otilde;rguloa tingimuste muutmise kavatsusest ja p&otilde;hjendab oma kavatsust v&auml;hemalt kolm kuud enne tingimuste muutmise otsustamist, kui seaduses ei ole s&auml;testatud teistsugust t&auml;htaega. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) The Communications Board shall inform the holder of a cable network licence of the intention to amend the conditions of the cable network licence on the basis of subsection (1) of this section and justify its decision in writing at least three months before making the decision on amendment, unless other term is specified by law. </inglise>
<eesti>(3) Kaabelleviv&otilde;rguloa omanik v&otilde;ib kahe kuu jooksul esitada Sideametile kirjaliku arvamuse kavandatavate muudatuste kohta, kui Sideamet ei ole arvamuse esitamiseks andnud pikemat t&auml;htaega. </eesti>
<inglise>(3) The holder of a cable network licence may submit a written opinion concerning the planned amendments to the Communications Board within two months unless the Communications Board has specified a longer term therefor. </inglise>
<eesti>(4) Sideamet vaatab t&auml;htaegselt laekunud arvamuse l&auml;bi ja teatab selle esitajale arvamuse esitamisest &uuml;he kuu jooksul kirjalikult oma seisukoha selle suhtes ning p&otilde;hjendab oma seisukohta. </eesti>
<inglise>(4) The Communications Board shall review the opinion received in time and shall notify the person who presented the opinion of its position thereon in writing and justify its position within one month after the presentation of the opinion. </inglise>
<eesti>(5) Ajavahemik kaabelleviv&otilde;rguloa tingimuste muutmise otsustamisest kaabelleviv&otilde;rguloa omanikule teatamise ja muudatuste j&otilde;ustumise vahel peab olema kuus kuud, kui k&auml;esolevas seaduses ei ole s&auml;testatud teistsugust t&auml;htaega. </eesti>
<inglise>(5) The period between the notification of the holder of a cable network licence of the decision to amend the conditions of the cable network licence and the entry into force of the amendments shall be six months unless another term is provided by this Act. </inglise>
<eesti>(6) Kaabelleviv&otilde;rguloa omanik v&otilde;ib esitada Sideametile taotluse kaabelleviv&otilde;rguloa tingimuste muutmiseks. </eesti>
<inglise>(6) The holder of a cable network licence may file an application with the Communications Board for the amendment of the conditions of the cable network licence. </inglise>
<eesti>Sideamet on kohustatud otsustama tingimuste muutmise v&otilde;i muutmata j&auml;tmise ning saatma Sideameti peadirektori vastava k&auml;skkirja v&auml;ljav&otilde;tte taotluse esitajale &uuml;he kuu jooksul, arvates taotluse esitamisest. </eesti>
<inglise>The Communications Board is required to decide the amendment of or refusal to amend the conditions and send an extract from the corresponding directive of the Director General of the Communications Board to the applicant within one month after the filing of the application. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 17. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 17. </inglise>
<eesti>Kaabelleviv&otilde;rguloa kehtivuse l&otilde;ppemine ja kehtetuks tunnistamine </eesti>
<inglise>Termination of validity and revocation of cable network licences </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Kaabelleviv&otilde;rguloa kehtivus l&otilde;peb: </eesti>
<inglise>(1) The validity of a cable network licence shall terminate: </inglise>
<eesti>1) kehtivust&auml;htaja m&ouml;&ouml;dumisel, kui enne selle t&auml;htaja l&otilde;ppemist ei ole kaabelleviv&otilde;rguluba pikendatud; </eesti>
<inglise>1) upon expiry of the validity of a cable network licence, if the licence has not been renewed before the expiry of its validity; </inglise>
<eesti>2) f&uuml;&uuml;silisest isikust kaabelleviv&otilde;rguloa omaniku surmaga v&otilde;i teov&otilde;imetuks tunnistamisega; </eesti>
<inglise>2) upon the death of a natural person who is the holder of the cable network licence, or divestment of active legal capacity of the natural person; </inglise>
<eesti>3) juriidilisest isikust kaabelleviv&otilde;rguloa omaniku l&otilde;ppemisega; </eesti>
<inglise>3) upon the dissolution of a legal person who is the holder of the cable network licence; </inglise>
<eesti>4) kaabelleviv&otilde;rguloa kehtetuks tunnistamisega; </eesti>
<inglise>4) upon revocation of the cable network licence; </inglise>
<eesti>5) kaabelleviv&otilde;rguloa omaniku taotluse alusel, kui ta ei soovi enam tegevusloaga m&auml;&auml;ratud tegevusalal tegutseda v&otilde;i </eesti>
<inglise>5) on the basis of an application of the holder of the cable network licence if the holder of the licence does not wish to continue operation in the field of activity specified in the licence, or </inglise>
<eesti>6) kaabelleviv&otilde;rgu v&otilde;&otilde;randamisel teisele isikule k&auml;esoleva seaduse &sect; 10 l&otilde;ikes 4 s&auml;testatud erisusega. </eesti>
<inglise>6) upon transfer of the cable network to another person with the specifications provided for in subsection 10 (4) of this Act. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Sideamet v&otilde;ib tunnistada kaabelleviv&otilde;rguloa kehtetuks, kui loale m&auml;rgitud isik: </eesti>
<inglise>(2) The Communications Board may revoke a cable network licence if the person specified in the licence: </inglise>
<eesti>1) ei t&auml;ida kaabelleviv&otilde;rguloaga m&auml;&auml;ratud tingimusi; </eesti>
<inglise>1) fails to comply with the conditions specified by the cable network licence; </inglise>
<eesti>2) ei t&auml;ida oma tegevuses k&auml;esolevast seadusest tulenevaid n&otilde;udeid; </eesti>
<inglise>2) fails to comply with the requirements arising from this Act in the person's activity; </inglise>
<eesti>3) esitas Sideametile valeandmeid; </eesti>
<inglise>3) has submitted false information to the Communications Board; </inglise>
<eesti>4) kahjustab oma tegevuse v&otilde;i tegevusetusega samas kaabelleviv&otilde;rgu piirkonnas programmide vastuv&otilde;tmist v&otilde;i edastamist teiste &otilde;iguslikul alusel rajatud kaabelleviv&otilde;rkude, &uuml;hisantennis&uuml;steemide v&otilde;i individuaalvastuv&otilde;tus&uuml;steemide kaudu v&otilde;i </eesti>
<inglise>4) prejudices, by act or omission, the reception or transmission of programmes within the same cable network area through other cable networks, by master antenna systems or individual reception systems constructed on a legal basis; or </inglise>
<eesti>5) tekitab raadioh&auml;ireid. </eesti>
<inglise>5) creates radio interference. </inglise>
<eesti>(3) Sideameti peadirektor tunnistab kaabelleviv&otilde;rguloa kehtetuks k&auml;skkirjaga, milles on &auml;ra n&auml;idatud ja p&otilde;hjendatud loa kehtetuks tunnistamise &otilde;iguslik alus. </eesti>
<inglise>(3) The Ministry of Culture shall revoke a cable network licence by a directive indicating and justifying the legal basis for the revocation. </inglise>
<eesti>(4) Kaabelleviv&otilde;rguloa kehtetuks tunnistamise k&auml;skkirja v&auml;ljav&otilde;te v&auml;ljastatakse kaabelleviv&otilde;rguloa omanikule. </eesti>
<inglise>(4) A copy of the directive by which a cable network licence is revoked shall be issued to the holder of the cable network licence. </inglise>
<eesti>3. peat&uuml;kk </eesti>
<inglise>Chapter 3 </inglise>
<eesti>&Uuml;hisantennis&uuml;steemi registreerimine </eesti>
<inglise>Registration of Master Antenna System </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 18. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 18. </inglise>
<eesti>&Uuml;hisantennis&uuml;steemi registreerimine </eesti>
<inglise>Registration of master antenna system </inglise>
<eesti>(1) &Uuml;hisantennis&uuml;steemi omanik peab kaabelleviteenuse osutamiseks registreerima &uuml;hisantennis&uuml;steemi Sideametis. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) In order to provide cable distribution services, the owner of a master antenna system shall register the master antenna system at the Communications Board. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) &Uuml;hisantennis&uuml;steemi registreerimiseks saadab &uuml;hisantennis&uuml;steemi omanik Sideametile registreerimisteatise, milles peab sisalduma: </eesti>
<inglise>(2) In order to register a master antenna system, the owner of a master antenna system shall send a registration notice to the Communications Board and the notice shall include: </inglise>
<eesti>1) omaniku nimi ja isiku- v&otilde;i registrikood; </eesti>
<inglise>1) name and personal identification code or register code of the owner; </inglise>
<eesti>2) aadress ja muud kontaktandmed; </eesti>
<inglise>2) the address and other details; </inglise>
<eesti>3) &uuml;hisantennis&uuml;steemi asukoha aadress; </eesti>
<inglise>3) the address of the location of the master antenna system; </inglise>
<eesti>4) tegevuse alustamise aeg. </eesti>
<inglise>4) commencement date of activity. </inglise>
<eesti>(3) &Uuml;hisantennis&uuml;steemi registreerimisteatisele tuleb lisada: </eesti>
<inglise>(3) The following shall be appended to a registration notice of a master antenna system: </inglise>
<eesti>1) juriidilisel isikul v&otilde;i f&uuml;&uuml;silisest isikust ettev&otilde;tjal t&otilde;estatud v&auml;ljav&otilde;te registrist, kus isik on registreeritud, v&otilde;i juriidilise isiku asutamisel s&otilde;lmitud asutamislepingu t&otilde;estatud &auml;rakiri; </eesti>
<inglise>1) in case of a legal person or a sole proprietor, a certified extract of the register in which the person is registered, or a certified copy of the memorandum of association of a legal person; </inglise>
<eesti>2) riigil&otilde;ivu tasumist t&otilde;endav dokument; </eesti>
<inglise>2) a document certifying payment of the state fee; </inglise>
<eesti>3) &uuml;hisantennis&uuml;steemi kirjeldus. </eesti>
<inglise>3) a description of the master antenna system. </inglise>
<eesti>(4) Sideamet registreerib k&auml;esoleva paragrahvi l&otilde;ikes 1 nimetatud &uuml;hisantennis&uuml;steemi ja saadab teatise esitajale Sideameti peadirektori vastava k&auml;skkirja v&auml;ljav&otilde;tte nelja n&auml;dala jooksul, arvates n&otilde;uetekohase teatise ja k&otilde;igi n&otilde;utavate dokumentide laekumisest Sideametile. </eesti>
<inglise>(4) The Communications Board shall register a master antenna system specified in subsection (1) of this section and shall send an extract from the corresponding directive of the Director General of the Communications Board to the notifier within four weeks after the receipt of a correctly completed application and all necessary documents at the Communications Board. </inglise>
<eesti>(5) Sideamet v&otilde;ib keelduda k&auml;esoleva paragrahvi l&otilde;ikes 1 nimetatud &uuml;hisantennis&uuml;steemi registreerimisest juhul, kui: </eesti>
<inglise>(5) The Communications Board may refuse to register a master antenna system specified in subsection (1) of this section, if: </inglise>
<eesti>1) ei ole tagatud kehtestatud n&otilde;uete t&auml;itmine v&otilde;i </eesti>
<inglise>1) compliance with the established requirements is not ensured, or </inglise>
<eesti>2) teatis v&otilde;i sellele lisatud dokumendid ei vasta kehtestatud n&otilde;uetele v&otilde;i teatisele ei ole lisatud k&auml;esolevas seaduses s&auml;testatud dokumente. </eesti>
<inglise>2) the notice or the annexed documents do not conform with the established requirements or the documents provided for in this Act are not appended to the notice. </inglise>
<eesti>(6) K&auml;esoleva paragrahvi l&otilde;ikes 1 nimetatud isik v&otilde;ib alustada kaabelleviteenuse osutamist p&auml;rast &uuml;hisantennis&uuml;steemi registreerimist Sideametis. </eesti>
<inglise>(6) The persons specified in subsection (1) of this section may commence the provision of cable distribution services after the master antenna system has been registered in the Communications Board. </inglise>
<eesti>(7) &Uuml;hisantennis&uuml;steemi registreerimise teatise vormi kehtestab teede- ja sideminister. </eesti>
<inglise>(7) The standard format for registration notices of master antenna systems shall be established by the Minister of Transport and Communications. </inglise>
<eesti>4. peat&uuml;kk </eesti>
<inglise>Chapter 4 </inglise>
<eesti>Kaabelleviv&otilde;rgu loomine, arendamine ja kasutamine ning kaabelleviteenuse osutamine </eesti>
<inglise>Creation, Development and Use of Cable Networks and Provision of Cable Distribution Services </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 19. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 19. </inglise>
<eesti>Kaabelleviv&otilde;rgu kasutamise ja kaabelleviteenuse osutamise kohustuslikud tingimused </eesti>
<inglise>Mandatory conditions for use of cable networks and provision of cable distribution services </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Kaabelleviv&otilde;rguloa omanik peab tagama j&auml;rgmiste programmide pideva edastamise kaabellevi programmide p&otilde;hipaketis: </eesti>
<inglise>(1) The holder of a cable network licence shall ensure the continuous transmission of the following programmes within the basic package of programmes distributed by cable: </inglise>
<eesti>1) Eesti avalik-&otilde;iguslike ringh&auml;&auml;linguorganisatsioonide programmid; </eesti>
<inglise>1) programmes of Estonian public service broadcasters; </inglise>
<eesti>2) maapealsete ringh&auml;&auml;lingusaatjate poolt edastatavad ja kaabelleviv&otilde;rguloaga m&auml;&auml;ratud piirkonnas tehnilistele n&otilde;uetele vastava signaalitugevuse juures vastuv&otilde;etavad televisiooniprogrammid, mille edastamise eest programmi omanik ei n&otilde;ua tasu. </eesti>
<inglise>2) television programmes transmitted by terrestrial broadcasting transmitters within an area specified in the cable network licence that are received at a signal intensity compatible with the technical requirements and for the transmission of which the owner requires no charge. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Kaabelleviv&otilde;rguloa omanik v&otilde;i kaabelleviteenuse osutaja peab tarbijale tagama kaabelleviteenuse &ouml;&ouml;p&auml;ev l&auml;bi v&otilde;i programmide eetrisoleku ajalise mahu ulatuses, kui lepingu pooled ei ole kokku leppinud teisiti. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) The holder of a cable network licence or the provider of cable distribution services shall ensure the consumers with cable distribution services throughout the twenty-four hour period or to the extent of the duration of the broadcasting time unless the parties agree otherwise. </inglise>
<eesti>(3) Enda loodud programmide edastamiseks peab kaabelleviv&otilde;rguloa omanikul v&otilde;i kaabelleviteenuse osutajal olema ringh&auml;&auml;linguseaduses (RT I 1994, 42, 680; 66, 1145; 1995, 83, 1437; 97, 1664; 1996, 49, 953; 1997, 29, 448; 52, 834; 93, 1564; 1998, 2, 42 ja 44; 1999, 16, 268; 25, 364; 59, 613; 2000, 25, 143; 35, 220; 102, 666) s&auml;testatud ringh&auml;&auml;linguluba. </eesti>
<inglise>(3) To transmit their own programmes, holders of cable network licences and providers of cable distribution services shall hold a broadcasting licence provided for in the Broadcasting Act (RT I 1994, 42, 680; 66, 1145; 1995, 83, 1437; 97, 1664; 1996, 49, 953; 1997, 29, 448; 52, 834; 93, 1564; 1998, 2, 42 and 44; 1999, 16, 268; 25, 364; 59, 613; 2000, 25, 143; 35, 220; 102, 666). </inglise>
<eesti>(4) K&auml;esoleva paragrahvi l&otilde;ike 1 punktis 2 s&auml;testatud tehnilised n&otilde;uded kehtestab teede- ja sideminister. </eesti>
<inglise>(4) Technical requirements for performance of the obligations provided for in clause (1) 2) of this section shall be established by the Minister of Transport and Communications. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 20. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 20. </inglise>
<eesti>Liitumislepingu v&otilde;i teenuse osutamise lepingu s&otilde;lmimine ja liitumine kaabelleviv&otilde;rguga </eesti>
<inglise>Entry into subscription contracts and contracts for provision of services and subscription to cable network </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Kaabelleviv&otilde;rguloa omanik v&otilde;i kaabelleviteenuse osutaja peab teatama avalduse esitanud isikule kaabelleviv&otilde;rguga liitumise ja kaabelleviteenuse osutamise v&otilde;imalusest ning t&auml;htaegadest 15 p&auml;eva jooksul, arvates avalduse esitamise kuup&auml;evast. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) The holder of a cable network licence or provider of cable distribution services shall inform a person who has submitted an application of the possibility of subscribing to a cable network and the provision of cable distribution services and of corresponding terms within fifteen days of the date on which the application was submitted. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Tarbija liitumisel kaabelleviv&otilde;rguga s&otilde;lmitakse tema ja kaabelleviv&otilde;rguloa omaniku vahel kirjalik liitumisleping, mis peab s&auml;testama poolte vastastikused &otilde;igused ja kohustused, sealhulgas: </eesti>
<inglise>(2) When a consumer subscribes to a cable network, a written subscription contract is entered into between the consumer and the holder of a cable network licence, which shall provide for the mutual rights and obligations of the parties, including: </inglise>
<eesti>1) kaabelleviv&otilde;rguga liitumise viisi, t&auml;htaja ja selle eest makstava tasu; </eesti>
<inglise>1) the manner of and the term and charge for connection to the cable network; </inglise>
<eesti>2) &uuml;henduse korrashoiu ja selle eest makstava tasu; </eesti>
<inglise>2) connection maintenance and charge therefor; </inglise>
<eesti>3) p&otilde;hipaketis edastatavate programmide nimetused; </eesti>
<inglise>3) titles of the programs transmitted within the basic package of programmes; </inglise>
<eesti>4) kasutamiseks lubatud vastuv&otilde;tuseadmete liigid; </eesti>
<inglise>4) types of receiving equipment the use of which is permitted; </inglise>
<eesti>5) kaabelleviv&otilde;rgu &uuml;henduspunkti asukoha; </eesti>
<inglise>5) the location of the connection point of the cable network; </inglise>
<eesti>6) kaabelleviteenuse eest makstava tasu; </eesti>
<inglise>6) the charge for the use of cable distribution services; </inglise>
<eesti>7) k&auml;esoleva l&otilde;ike punktides 1, 2 ja 6 nimetatud tasu maksmise korra; </eesti>
<inglise>7) the procedure for the payment of the charge specified in clauses 1), 2) and 6) of this subsection. </inglise>
<eesti>8) lepingu muutmise ja t&auml;iendamise korra ning poolte vastutuse; </eesti>
<inglise>8) the procedure for amendment of the contract, and the liabilities of the parties; </inglise>
<eesti>9) kaebuste esitamise ja vaidluste lahendamise korra. </eesti>
<inglise>9) procedure for submission of complaints and resolution of disputes. </inglise>
<eesti>(3) P&otilde;hipaketti mittekuuluvate programmide edastamiseks tarbija avalduse alusel s&otilde;lmitav kirjalik teenuse osutamise leping peab s&auml;testama poolte vastastikused &otilde;igused ja kohustused, sealhulgas: </eesti>
<inglise>(3) A written contract for provision of services entered into on application of a consumer for the transmission of programs not included in the basic package of programs shall provide for mutual rights and obligations, including: </inglise>
<eesti>1) paketis edastatavate programmide nimetused; </eesti>
<inglise>1) titles of the programs transmitted within the package of programmes; </inglise>
<eesti>2) kaabelleviteenuse kasutamise eest makstava tasu; </eesti>
<inglise>2) the charge for the use of cable distribution services; </inglise>
<eesti>3) lepingu muutmise ja t&auml;iendamise korra ning poolte vastutuse; </eesti>
<inglise>3) the procedure for amendment of the contract, and the liabilities of the parties; </inglise>
<eesti>4) kaebuste esitamise ja vaidluste lahendamise korra. </eesti>
<inglise>4) the procedure for submission of complaints and resolution of disputes. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 21. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 21. </inglise>
<eesti>Vastuv&otilde;tuseadme &uuml;hendamine kaabelleviv&otilde;rguga </eesti>
<inglise>Connection of receiving equipment to cable network </inglise>
<eesti>Kaabelleviv&otilde;rguloa omanik peab tagama vastuv&otilde;tuseadme &uuml;hendamise kaabelleviv&otilde;rguga 10 t&ouml;&ouml;p&auml;eva jooksul, arvates liitumislepingu s&otilde;lmimisest, kui lepingu osapooled ei ole kokku leppinud teisiti. </eesti>
<inglise>The holder of a cable network licence shall enable connection of receiving equipment with the cable network within ten working days after the entry into the subscription contract unless the parties to the contract have agreed otherwise. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 22. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 22. </inglise>
<eesti>Kaabelleviteenuse osutamise piiramine ja peatamine </eesti>
<inglise>Restriction and suspension of provision of cable distribution services </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Kaabelleviv&otilde;rguloa omanik v&otilde;i kaabelleviteenuse osutaja v&otilde;ib tarbijale kaabelleviteenuse osutamist piirata v&otilde;i selle peatada juhul, kui: </eesti>
<inglise>(1) The holder of a cable network licence or the provider of a cable distribution service may restrict or suspend the provision of cable distribution services to a consumer; if: </inglise>
<eesti>1) tarbija ei ole tasunud temale osutatud teenuse eest &otilde;igeaegselt; </eesti>
<inglise>1) the consumer has failed to pay for the provided services in a timely manner; </inglise>
<eesti>2) tarbija on kaabelleviv&otilde;rguga &uuml;hendanud mittet&ouml;&ouml;korras v&otilde;i n&otilde;uetele mittevastava vastuv&otilde;tuseadme; </eesti>
<inglise>2) the consumer has connected to the cable network receiving equipment which is not in compliance with the requirements or is not in working order; </inglise>
<eesti>3) tarbija h&auml;irib vastuv&otilde;tuseadme kasutamisega kaabelleviv&otilde;rgu t&ouml;&ouml;d; </eesti>
<inglise>3) the consumer interferes with the work of the cable network by his or her use of the receiving equipment; </inglise>
<eesti>4) kaabelleviteenuse osutamise piiramine v&otilde;i peatamine on vajalik kaabelleviv&otilde;rgu seadme v&otilde;i rajatise paigaldamiseks, remondiks, vahetamiseks v&otilde;i hooldamiseks; </eesti>
<inglise>4) the restriction or suspension of the provision of the cable distribution service is necessary for the installation, repair, exchange or maintenance of cable network equipment or facilities; </inglise>
<eesti>5) tarbija rikub liitumislepingu v&otilde;i teenuse osutamise lepingu tingimusi v&otilde;i </eesti>
<inglise>5) the consumer breaches the conditions of the subscription contract or contract for provision of services; or </inglise>
<eesti>6) tarbija on liitumislepingu v&otilde;i teenuse osutamise lepingu s&otilde;lmimisel esitanud eba&otilde;igeid andmeid v&otilde;i dokumente. </eesti>
<inglise>6) the consumer has submitted incorrect information upon entry into the subscription contract or contract for provision of services. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Kaabelleviv&otilde;rguloa omanik v&otilde;ib kaabelleviteenuse osutamist piirata v&otilde;i selle peatada &uuml;ksnes siis, kui ta on tarbijale sellest teatanud v&auml;hemalt viis t&ouml;&ouml;p&auml;eva enne kaabelleviteenuse osutamise piiramist v&otilde;i peatamist, teatades &uuml;htlasi piiramise v&otilde;i peatamise aja ning p&otilde;hjused, v&auml;lja arvatud k&auml;esoleva paragrahvi l&otilde;ike 1 punktides 2 ja 3 s&auml;testatud juhtudel, kui on vaja kohe kaabelleviteenuse osutamist piirata v&otilde;i see peatada. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) The holder of a cable network licence may restrict or suspend the provision of cable distribution services only if the holder of the licence has informed the consumer thereof at least five working days before the restriction or suspension of the cable distribution services, and shall notify the duration of and reasons for the restriction or suspension, except if the immediate restriction or suspension of the cable distribution services is necessary in the cases provided for in clauses (1) 2) and 3) of this section. </inglise>
<eesti>(3) Kaabelleviteenuse osutamist ei v&otilde;i piirata ega peatada, kui tarbija k&otilde;rvaldab enne kaabelleviteenuse osutamise piiramise v&otilde;i peatamise algust kavandatava piiramise v&otilde;i peatamise aluseks olnud asjaolu ning on sellest teavitanud kaabelleviv&otilde;rguloa omanikku v&otilde;i kaabelleviteenuse osutajat. </eesti>
<inglise>(3) The provision of cable network services shall not be restricted or suspended if a consumer eliminates the circumstances underlying the restriction or suspension prior to the application of the planned restriction or suspension of the provision of cable network services and informs the holder of the cable network licence or provider of cable distribution services thereof. </inglise>
<eesti>(4) Kaabelleviv&otilde;rguloa omanik v&otilde;i kaabelleviteenuse osutaja ei v&otilde;i piirata ega peatada kaabelleviteenuse osutamist, kui tarbija vaidlustab kirjalikult osutatud kaabelleviteenuse tasu suuruse enne makset&auml;htp&auml;eva saabumist ning tasub &otilde;igeaegselt osutatud kaabelleviteenuste eest osas, milles ta tasu ei vaidlusta. </eesti>
<inglise>(4) The holder of a cable network licence or provider of cable distribution services shall not restrict or suspend the provision of cable distribution services if a consumer contests the cable distribution service charge notified in writing, prior to the payment term, and makes a timely payment for the part of the cable network services the charge for which he or she does not contest. </inglise>
<eesti>(5) Kui k&auml;esoleva paragrahvi l&otilde;ikes 4 nimetatud tasu ja selle suuruse vaidlustamine ning tasu osaline tasumata j&auml;tmine tarbija poolt osutub alusetuks, on tarbija kohustatud tasumata summa tasuma hiljemalt j&auml;rgmiseks makset&auml;htp&auml;evaks. </eesti>
<inglise>(5) If the contestation by a subscriber of the charge specified in subsection (4) of this section and of the amount thereof, and the fact that the consumer has not paid for the contested part of is found to be without legal basis, the consumer shall pay the unpaid amount not later than by the following due date for payment. </inglise>
<eesti>(6) Kui kaabelleviteenuse osutamise piiramine v&otilde;i peatamine toimus k&auml;esoleva paragrahvi l&otilde;ike 1 punkti 4 alusel, ei v&otilde;eta selle perioodi eest tarbijalt tasu. </eesti>
<inglise>(6) If the provision of cable distribution services is restricted or suspended on the basis of clause (1) 4) of this section, a charge is not collected from the consumers for such period. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 23. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 23. </inglise>
<eesti>Liitumislepingu v&otilde;i teenuse osutamise lepingu peatamine ning l&otilde;petamine </eesti>
<inglise>Suspension and termination of subscription contracts and contracts for provision of services </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Tarbijal on &otilde;igus peatada liitumisleping v&otilde;i teenuse osutamise leping tema poolt soovitud ajaks &uuml;hest kuust kuni &uuml;he aastani, teatades sellest v&auml;hemalt 10 p&auml;eva ette, kui ta on t&auml;itnud kaabelleviv&otilde;rguloa omaniku v&otilde;i kaabelleviteenuse osutaja ees k&otilde;ik liitumislepingust v&otilde;i teenuse osutamise lepingust tulenevad kohustused. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) The consumer has the right to suspend the subscription contract or contract for provision of services for a period of one month up to one year at his or her discretion by notifying thereof at least ten days in advance provided that the consumer has performed all obligations arising from the subscription contract or contract for provision of services in respect of the holder of a cable network licence or provider of cable distribution services. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Liitumislepingu peatamisel: </eesti>
<inglise>(2) Upon suspension of subscription contract: </inglise>
<eesti>1) peatatakse kaabelleviteenuse osutamine; </eesti>
<inglise>1) the provision of cable distribution services is suspended; </inglise>
<eesti>2) vastuv&otilde;tuseade v&otilde;i selle &uuml;hendus &uuml;hendatakse kaabelleviv&otilde;rgust lahti; </eesti>
<inglise>2) receiving equipment or its connection is disconnected from the cable network; </inglise>
<eesti>3) tarbija ei pea maksma kaabelleviteenuse osutamise selle aja eest, millal leping oli peatatud; </eesti>
<inglise>3) the consumer is not required to pay for the provision of the cable distribution services for the time during which the contract is suspended; </inglise>
<eesti>4) kaabelleviv&otilde;rguloa omanik v&otilde;i kaabelleviteenuse osutaja v&otilde;ib v&otilde;rgu vastuv&otilde;tuseadme &uuml;hendamiseks v&otilde;i teenuse osutamiseks vajalikud seadmed, mis kuuluvad kaabelleviv&otilde;rguloa omanikule v&otilde;i kaabelleviteenuse osutajale, anda kasutamiseks teisele tarbijale. </eesti>
<inglise>4) the holder of a cable network licence or provider of cable distribution services may give the equipment necessary for connection to the receiving equipment or provision of services belonging to the holder of a cable network licence or provider of cable distribution services to another consumer for use. </inglise>
<eesti>(3) Teenuse osutamise lepingu peatamisel: </eesti>
<inglise>(3) Upon suspension of contract for provision of services: </inglise>
<eesti>1) peatatakse kaabelleviteenuse osutamine; </eesti>
<inglise>1) the provision of cable distribution services is suspended; </inglise>
<eesti>2) tarbija ei pea maksma kaabelleviteenuse osutamise selle aja eest, millal leping oli peatatud. </eesti>
<inglise>2) the consumer is not required to pay for the provision of the cable distribution services for the time during which the contract is suspended. </inglise>
<eesti>(4) Kui liitumislepingu v&otilde;i teenuse osutamise lepingu peatamine l&otilde;petatakse, peab kaabelleviv&otilde;rguloa omanik v&otilde;i kaabelleviteenuse osutaja tarbija vastava avalduse alusel j&auml;tkama kaabelleviteenuse osutamist viie t&ouml;&ouml;p&auml;eva jooksul. </eesti>
<inglise>(4) If the suspension of a subscription contract or contract for provision of services is terminated, the holder of a cable network licence or provider of cable distribution services shall, on the basis of a corresponding application, continue the provision of the cable distribution services within five working days. </inglise>
<eesti>(5) Tarbijal on &otilde;igus liitumisleping v&otilde;i teenuse osutamise leping l&otilde;petada, teavitades sellest kaabelleviv&otilde;rgu omanikku v&otilde;i kaabelleviteenuse osutajat 10 p&auml;eva ette. </eesti>
<inglise>(5) A consumer has the right to terminate a subscription contract or contract for provision of services by notifying the holder of a cable network licence or provider of cable distribution services thereof ten days in advance. </inglise>
<eesti>(6) Kaabelleviv&otilde;rguloa omanikul v&otilde;i kaabelleviteenuse osutajal on &otilde;igus liitumisleping v&otilde;i teenuse osutamise leping l&otilde;petada, kui: </eesti>
<inglise>(6) The holder of a cable network licence or provider of cable distribution services has the right to terminate a subscription contract or contract for provision of services, if: </inglise>
<eesti>1) &uuml;letatakse k&auml;esoleva paragrahvi l&otilde;ikes 1 nimetatud t&auml;htaeg v&otilde;i </eesti>
<inglise>1) the term specified in subsection (1) of this section has expired, or; </inglise>
<eesti>2) kaabelleviteenuse osutamist on piiratud v&otilde;i see on peatatud k&auml;esoleva seaduse &sect; 22 l&otilde;ike 1 punktide 1-3, 5 v&otilde;i 6 alusel ning piiramise v&otilde;i peatamise alus ei ole &auml;ra langenud &uuml;he kuu jooksul. </eesti>
<inglise>2) the provision of cable distribution services is restricted or suspended pursuant to clauses 22 (1) 1) -3), 5) and 6) of this Act and the grounds for the restriction or suspension continue to exist after one month has passed. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 24. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 24. </inglise>
<eesti>Liitumislepingust tulenevate &otilde;iguste ja kohustuste &uuml;leminek kaabelleviv&otilde;rgu omaniku vahetumisel </eesti>
<inglise>Transfer of rights and obligations arising from subscription contract upon change of owner of cable network </inglise>
<eesti>Kaabelleviv&otilde;rgu omandi&otilde;iguse &uuml;leminekul teisele isikule j&auml;&auml;b liitumisleping j&otilde;usse ka uue omaniku suhtes, kui kaabelleviv&otilde;rgu uus omanik ja tarbija ei lepi kokku teisiti. </eesti>
<inglise>Upon the transfer of the right of ownership in a cable network from one person to another, the subscription contract shall remain in force with regard to the new owner, unless the new owner of the cable network and consumer agree otherwise. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 25. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 25. </inglise>
<eesti>Kaabelleviv&otilde;rgu rikete k&otilde;rvaldamine </eesti>
<inglise>Elimination of breakdowns in cable network </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Kaabelleviv&otilde;rguloa omanik peab korraldama tarbijatelt rikketeadete vastuv&otilde;tmise, teavitama tarbijaid teadete vastuv&otilde;tmise korrast ja aegadest ning konkreetse rikke k&otilde;rvaldamise t&auml;htajast. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) The holder of a cable network licence shall organise receipt of information concerning breakdowns from consumers, inform the consumers of the procedure and time for receipt of such information and of the term for elimination of the breakdown. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Tarbija peab kaabelleviv&otilde;rgu rikke korral v&otilde;imaldama kaabelleviv&otilde;rguloa omaniku esindajale juurdep&auml;&auml;su kaabelleviv&otilde;rgu osaks olevale seadmele ja vastuv&otilde;tuseadmele nende kontrollimiseks ja rikke asukoha selgitamiseks. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) In the case of a breakdown of the cable network, a consumer shall allow representatives of the holder of the cable network licence access to equipment which forms a part of the cable network and to receiving equipment in order to carry out checks and to locate the breakdown. </inglise>
<eesti>(3) Kaabelleviv&otilde;rguloa omanik on kohustatud rikkest teadasaamisel korraldama kaabelleviv&otilde;rgu ja tarbija vastuv&otilde;tuseadme &uuml;henduse rikke k&otilde;rvaldamise hiljemalt rikkest teatamise p&auml;evale j&auml;rgneva t&ouml;&ouml;p&auml;eva jooksul. </eesti>
<inglise>(3) Upon receiving notification of a breakdown, the holder of the cable network licence shall arrange for the elimination of a breakdown of the connection between the cable network and the receiving equipment of a consumer during the working day following the date of notification of the breakdown. </inglise>
<eesti>(4) Tarbijale kuuluva vastuv&otilde;tuseadme &uuml;henduse ja vastuv&otilde;tuseadme rikke k&otilde;rvaldamise kulud kannab tarbija, v&auml;lja arvatud juhul, kui rikke tekkimises on s&uuml;&uuml;di kaabelleviv&otilde;rguloa omanik. </eesti>
<inglise>(4) Expenses incurred in the elimination of breakdowns in receiving equipment and connections to receiving equipment shall be borne by the consumer, except if the holder of a cable network licence has caused the breakdown. </inglise>
<eesti>5. peat&uuml;kk </eesti>
<inglise>Chapter 5 </inglise>
<eesti>J&auml;relevalve ja vastutus </eesti>
<inglise>Supervision and Liability </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 26. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 26. </inglise>
<eesti>Riiklik j&auml;relevalve seaduse t&auml;itmise &uuml;le </eesti>
<inglise>State supervision over compliance with law </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Riiklikku j&auml;relevalvet k&auml;esoleva seaduse ja sellest tulenevate &otilde;igusaktide t&auml;itmise &uuml;le teostab Sideamet. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) State supervision over compliance with this Act and legislation arising therefrom shall be exercised by the Communications Board. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Riiklikku j&auml;relevalvet teostavad ametnikud k&auml;esoleva seaduse t&auml;henduses on Sideameti peadirektor ja tema poolt j&auml;relevalve teostamiseks volitatud ametnik (edaspidi ametnik). </eesti>
<inglise>(2) For the purposes of this Act, officials exercising state supervision are the Director General of the Communications Board and the officials authorised to exercise supervision by the Director General (hereinafter officials). </inglise>
<eesti>(3) J&auml;relevalve teostamise k&auml;igus Sideamet: </eesti>
<inglise>(3) In the process of exercising supervision, the Communications Board shall: </inglise>
<eesti>1) kontrollib kaabelleviv&otilde;rgu ja &uuml;hisantennis&uuml;steemi vastavust &otilde;igusaktidega kehtestatud tehnilistele n&otilde;uetele; </eesti>
<inglise>1) monitor the compatibility of cable networks and master antenna systems with the technical requirements established by legislation; </inglise>
<eesti>2) kontrollib kaabelleviteenuse osutamise vastavust k&auml;esolevale seadusele. </eesti>
<inglise>2) monitor the compliance of the provision of cable distribution services with this Act. </inglise>
<eesti>(4) J&auml;relevalvet kaabelleviv&otilde;rgu loomise, arendamise ja kasutamise ning kaabelleviteenuse osutamise &uuml;le teostab Sideamet seaduse alusel ning teede- ja sideministri kehtestatud korras. </eesti>
<inglise>(4) The Communications Board shall exercise supervision over the creation, development and use of cable networks and the provision of cable distribution services pursuant to law and the procedure established by the Minister of Transport and Communications. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 27. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 27. </inglise>
<eesti>Ettekirjutus </eesti>
<inglise>Precepts </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Ametnikul on &otilde;igus teha kaabelleviv&otilde;rguloa, &uuml;hisantenni- v&otilde;i individuaalvastuv&otilde;tus&uuml;steemi omanikule kohustuslikke ettekirjutusi &otilde;iguserikkumise l&otilde;petamiseks, teatud toimingute sooritamiseks v&otilde;i tegevuse peatamiseks. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) Officials have the right to issue mandatory precepts to the holders of cable network licences and owners of master antenna systems or individual reception systems for the termination of an offence, for the performance of certain acts or suspension of activities. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) K&auml;esoleva paragrahvi l&otilde;ikes 1 nimetatud ettekirjutuses peab sisalduma: </eesti>
<inglise>(2) The precept specified in subsection (1) of this section shall include: </inglise>
<eesti>1) ettekirjutuse koostanud ametniku nimi ja ametikoht; </eesti>
<inglise>1) the name and position of the official who prepared the precept; </inglise>
<eesti>2) ettekirjutuse tegemise kuup&auml;ev; </eesti>
<inglise>2) the date of issue of the precept; </inglise>
<eesti>3) kaabelleviv&otilde;rguloa, &uuml;hisantenni- v&otilde;i individuaalvastuv&otilde;tus&uuml;steemi omaniku &auml;rinimi v&otilde;i nimi; </eesti>
<inglise>3) business name or name of the holder of a cable network licence or owner of a master antenna system or individual reception system. </inglise>
<eesti>4) &otilde;iguserikkumise koht; </eesti>
<inglise>4) the place of the offence; </inglise>
<eesti>5) ettekirjutuse tegemise &otilde;iguslikud alused ja ettekirjutuse tegemist tingivad asjaolud; </eesti>
<inglise>5) the legal bases for issue of the precept, and the circumstances underlying the issue of the precept; </inglise>
<eesti>6) ettekirjutuse t&auml;itmise t&auml;htaeg; </eesti>
<inglise>6) the term for compliance with the precept; </inglise>
<eesti>7) viide ettekirjutuse t&auml;itmata j&auml;tmisel rakendatavatele sanktsioonidele. </eesti>
<inglise>7) a reference to the sanctions to be applied in the case of failure to comply with the precept. </inglise>
<eesti>(3) Ettekirjutus antakse kaabelleviv&otilde;rguloa, &uuml;hisantenni- v&otilde;i individuaalvastuv&otilde;tus&uuml;steemi omanikule v&otilde;i tema esindajale k&auml;tte vahetult allkirja vastu v&otilde;i saadetakse posti teel v&auml;ljastusteatega. </eesti>
<inglise>(3) The precept shall be delivered directly to the holder of a cable network licence or owner of a master antenna system or individual reception system, or to a representative thereof against signature, or shall be delivered by post with a notice of delivery. </inglise>
<eesti>(4) Sideametil on ettekirjutuse tinginud asjaolude muutumisel &otilde;igus ettekirjutust muuta v&otilde;i see t&uuml;histada. </eesti>
<inglise>(4) The Communications Board have the right to amend or revoke a precept if circumstances underlying the issue of the precept have changed. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 28. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 28. </inglise>
<eesti>Seadusest tulenevate n&otilde;uete t&auml;itmise kontrollimine </eesti>
<inglise>Monitoring of compliance with requirements arising from law </inglise>
<eesti>(1) K&auml;esoleva seaduse ja selle alusel kehtestatud &otilde;igusaktide n&otilde;uete t&auml;itmise kontrollimiseks on ametnikul &otilde;igus kontrollida kaabelleviv&otilde;rgu, &uuml;hisantenni- v&otilde;i individuaalvastuv&otilde;tus&uuml;steemi tehnilist seisundit ning teha dokumentidest v&auml;ljav&otilde;tteid ja &auml;rakirju. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) In order to monitor compliance with requirements arising from this Act and legislation established on the basis thereof, officials have the right to inspect the technical conditions of cable networks, master antenna systems and individual reception systems and to make extracts from and copies of documents. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Raadioh&auml;irete kindlakstegemiseks v&otilde;i k&otilde;rvaldamiseks on kaabelleviv&otilde;rguloa, &uuml;hisantenni- v&otilde;i individuaalvastuv&otilde;tus&uuml;steemi omanik v&otilde;i tema esindaja kohustatud ametniku esimesel n&otilde;udmisel v&otilde;imaldama ametnikule juurdep&auml;&auml;su kaabelleviv&otilde;rgule, &uuml;hisantenni- v&otilde;i individuaalvastuv&otilde;tus&uuml;steemile. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) In order to establish or eliminate radio interference, the holder of a cable network licence or owner of a master antenna system or individual reception system or a representative thereof is required to allow the official access to the cable network, master antenna system or individual reception system at the first request of the official. </inglise>
<eesti>(3) Ametnik on kohustatud hoidma kontrollimise k&auml;igus talle teatavaks saanud kaabelleviv&otilde;rgu v&otilde;i &uuml;hisantennis&uuml;steemiga seotud konfidentsiaalset informatsiooni ning kasutama saadud teavet ainult riikliku j&auml;relevalve teostamisel. </eesti>
<inglise>(3) An official is required to maintain confidential information related to cable networks or master antenna systems which become known to him or her in the course of monitoring, and to use obtained information only in the exercise of state supervision. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 29. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 29. </inglise>
<eesti>Teabe andmise kohustus </eesti>
<inglise>Notification obligation </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Kaabelleviv&otilde;rguloa ja &uuml;hisantennis&uuml;steemi omanik on kohustatud teavitama Sideametit &uuml;he kuu jooksul kirjalikult enda kohta k&auml;ivates andmetes toimunud muudatustest, v&otilde;rreldes tema poolt Sideametile k&auml;esoleva seaduse alusel esitatud andmetega. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) The holder of a cable network licence or owner of a master antenna system is required to notify the Communications Board within one month in writing of any changes in the information pertaining to them as compared to the information communicated to the Communications Board by them pursuant to law. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Kaabelleviv&otilde;rguloa omanik on kohustatud iga aasta 1. veebruariks teavitama Sideametit eelmisel kalendriaastal kaabelleviv&otilde;rgus toimunud muudatustest ning eelmisel kalendriaastal temaga liitumislepingu s&otilde;lminud ja liitumislepingu l&otilde;petanud tarbijate arvust. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) The holder of a cable network licence is required to notify the Communications Board by 1 February each year of any changes involving the cable network during the previous calendar year and of the number of customers who entered into or terminated subscription contracts with the holder of the licence during the previous calendar year. </inglise>
<eesti>(3) Sideameti n&otilde;udel on kaabelleviv&otilde;rguloa, &uuml;hisantenni- v&otilde;i individuaalvastuv&otilde;tus&uuml;steemi omanik v&otilde;i tema esindaja kohustatud: </eesti>
<inglise>(3) At the request of the Communications Board, the holder of a cable network licence or owner of a master antenna system or individual reception system or a representative thereof is required to: </inglise>
<eesti>1) ilmuma Sideametisse selgituste andmiseks; </eesti>
<inglise>1) appear at the Communications Board to provide explanations; </inglise>
<eesti>2) esitama Sideametile tema valduses olevaid kaabelleviv&otilde;rgu, &uuml;hisantenni- v&otilde;i individuaalvastuv&otilde;tus&uuml;steemi tehnilisi projekte ning liitumislepinguid ja muid dokumente, mis puudutavad kaabelleviteenuse osutamisega seotud tegevust. </eesti>
<inglise>2) submit to the Communications Board technical designs and subscription contracts and other documents in its possession concerning the cable network, master antenna system or individual reception system which pertain to the activities related to cable distribution services. </inglise>
<eesti>(4) K&auml;esoleva paragrahvi l&otilde;igetes 1-3 nimetatud n&otilde;ude t&auml;itmata j&auml;tmisel v&otilde;ib Sideamet rakendada sunniraha asendust&auml;itmise ja sunniraha seaduses (RT I 2001, 50, 283) s&auml;testatud korras. </eesti>
<inglise>(4) Upon failure to comply with the requirements specified in subsections (1) -(3) of this section, the Communications Board may impose penalty payment pursuant to the procedure provided for in the Substitutive Enforcement and Penalty Payment Act (RT I 2001, 50, 283). </inglise>
<eesti>(5) K&auml;esoleva paragrahvi l&otilde;ikes 4 nimetatud sunniraha &uuml;lemm&auml;&auml;r on 10 000 krooni. </eesti>
<inglise>(5) The maximum rate of penalty payment specified in subsection (4) of this section is 10 000 kroons. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 30. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 30. </inglise>
<eesti>Juriidilise isiku haldusvastutus </eesti>
<inglise>Administrative liability of legal persons </inglise>
<eesti>Juriidilisele isikule kohaldatakse haldusvastutust j&auml;rgmiste &otilde;iguserikkumiste korral: </eesti>
<inglise>Administrative liability shall be imposed on a legal person for the following offences: </inglise>
<eesti>1) ilma k&auml;esoleva seaduse &sect;-s 10 s&auml;testatud kaabelleviv&otilde;rguloata kaabelleviv&otilde;rgu loomise, arendamise v&otilde;i kasutamise eest - m&auml;&auml;ratakse rahatrahv 10 000 kuni 1 000 000 krooni; </eesti>
<inglise>1) a fine of 10 000 up to 1 000 000 kroons is imposed for the creation, development or use of a cable network without a cable network licence specified in &sect; 10 of this Act; </inglise>
<eesti>2) &uuml;hisantennis&uuml;steemi abil kaabelleviteenuse osutamise eest ilma k&auml;esoleva seaduse &sect;-s 18 s&auml;testatud registreerimiseta, kui sama tegevuse l&otilde;petamiseks on tehtud ettekirjutus ja isik ei ole seda ettekirjutust t&auml;itnud, - m&auml;&auml;ratakse rahatrahv kuni 50 000 krooni; </eesti>
<inglise>2) a fine of up to 50 000 kroons is imposed for the provision of cable distribution services by master antenna system without the registration provided for in &sect; 18 of this Act, if a precept has been issued for the termination of such activity and the person has failed to comply with the precept; </inglise>
<eesti>3) kaabelleviv&otilde;rguloa omaniku v&otilde;i &uuml;hisantennis&uuml;steemi omaniku poolt Sideametile valeandmete esitamisel - m&auml;&auml;ratakse rahatrahv 5000 kuni 100 000 krooni; </eesti>
<inglise>3) a fine of 5000 up to 100 000 kroons is imposed for the submission of incorrect information by the holder of a cable network or owner of a master antenna system to the Communications Board; </inglise>
<eesti>4) kaabelleviv&otilde;rgu, &uuml;hisantenni- v&otilde;i individuaalvastuv&otilde;tus&uuml;steemi poolt raadioh&auml;irete tekitamise eest - m&auml;&auml;ratakse kaabelleviv&otilde;rgu, &uuml;hisantenni- v&otilde;i individuaalvastuv&otilde;tus&uuml;steemi omanikule rahatrahv 1000 kuni 50 000 krooni; </eesti>
<inglise>4) a fine of 1000 up to 50 000 kroons is imposed on the owner of a cable network, master antenna system or individual reception system for the creation of radio interference by the corresponding cable network, master antenna system or individual reception system; </inglise>
<eesti>5) k&auml;esoleva paragrahvi punktides 1-4 nimetamata, kuid k&auml;esolevast seadusest tulenevate n&otilde;uete rikkumise eest, kui sama teo v&otilde;i tegevusetuse l&otilde;petamiseks on tehtud ettekirjutus ja isik ei ole seda ettekirjutust t&auml;itnud, - m&auml;&auml;ratakse rahatrahv 1000 kuni 100 000 krooni. </eesti>
<inglise>5) a fine of 1000 up to 100 000 kroons is imposed for a violation of the requirements arising from this Act which are not specified in clauses 1) -4) of this section, if a precept has been issued for the termination of such act or omission and the person has failed to comply with the precept. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 31. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 31. </inglise>
<eesti>Haldus&otilde;iguserikkumise protokolli koostamine </eesti>
<inglise>Preparation of minutes of administrative offences </inglise>
<eesti>(1) K&auml;esoleva seaduse &sect;-s 30 s&auml;testatud haldus&otilde;iguserikkumiste kohta koostab haldus&otilde;iguserikkumise protokolli riiklikku j&auml;relevalvet teostav ametnik. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) Officials exercising state supervision shall prepare administrative offence reports concerning the administrative offences provided for in &sect; 30 of this Act. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Haldus&otilde;iguserikkumise protokolli m&auml;rgitakse j&auml;rgmised andmed: </eesti>
<inglise>(2) An administrative offence report shall set out the following information: </inglise>
<eesti>1) koostamise aeg ja koht; </eesti>
<inglise>1) the time and place of preparation; </inglise>
<eesti>2) selle ametiasutuse nimetus ja aadress, kes protokolli koostab; </eesti>
<inglise>2) the name and address of the agency which prepared the report; </inglise>
<eesti>3) protokolli koostanud isiku ametinimetus, ees- ja perekonnanimi; </eesti>
<inglise>3) the official title and the given name and surname of the person who prepared the report; </inglise>
<eesti>4) haldus&otilde;iguserikkuja nimetus v&otilde;i &auml;rinimi, registrikood ja asukoht; </eesti>
<inglise>4) the name or business name, registry code and seat of the administrative offender; </inglise>
<eesti>5) haldus&otilde;iguserikkuja esindaja ees- ja perekonnanimi ning ametikoht; </eesti>
<inglise>5) the given name, surname and position of the representative of the administrative offender; </inglise>
<eesti>6) haldus&otilde;iguserikkumise koht, aeg ja kirjeldus; </eesti>
<inglise>6) the place, time and description of the administrative offence; </inglise>
<eesti>7) viide k&auml;esoleva seaduse s&auml;tetele, mille alusel haldusvastutust kohaldatakse; </eesti>
<inglise>7) a reference to the provisions of this Act which are the bases for imposition of administrative liability; </inglise>
<eesti>8) haldus&otilde;iguserikkuja esindaja seletus v&otilde;i m&auml;rge seletuse andmisest loobumise kohta. </eesti>
<inglise>8) an explanation provided by the representative of the administrative offender or a notation concerning refusal to provide an explanation. </inglise>
<eesti>(3) Protokollile kirjutavad alla selle koostanud isik ja haldus&otilde;iguserikkuja esindaja. </eesti>
<inglise>(3) A report shall be signed by the person who prepares the report and the representative of the administrative offender. </inglise>
<eesti>Kui haldus&otilde;iguserikkuja esindaja keeldub protokollile alla kirjutamast, tehakse sellesse vastav kanne. </eesti>
<inglise>If the representative of the administrative offender refuses to sign the report, a corresponding entry shall be made therein. </inglise>
<eesti>Protokollile lisatakse haldus&otilde;iguserikkuja esindaja kirjalikud m&auml;rkused protokolli, samuti protokollile allakirjutamisest keeldumise kohta. </eesti>
<inglise>The written comments of the representative of the administrative offender concerning the report or refusal to sign the report shall be annexed to the report. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 32. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 32. </inglise>
<eesti>Menetlus juriidilise isiku haldus&otilde;iguserikkumise asjas </eesti>
<inglise>Proceedings in matters concerning administrative offences of legal persons </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Menetlus k&auml;esoleva seaduse &sect;-s 30 s&auml;testatud juriidilise isiku haldus&otilde;iguserikkumiste asjades, sealhulgas karistuse m&auml;&auml;ramine ja vaidlustamine, toimub haldus&otilde;iguserikkumiste seadustikus (RT 1992, 29, 396; RT I 1999, 41, 496; 45, &otilde;iend; 58, 608; 60, 616; 87, 792; 92, 825; 95, 843; 2000, 10, 58; 25, 141; 28, 167; 29, 169; 40, 247; 49, 301 ja 305; 51, 321; 54, 346, 348 ja 351; 55, 361; 58, 376; 84, 533; 86, 544 ja 548; 89, 578; 95, 609 ja 613; 2001, 3, 5; 17, 76; 18, 87; 21, 115 ja 116; 31, 174; 42, 236; 52, 303; 53, 312, 313 ja 314; 56, 333, 335 ja 339; 58, 356) ja t&auml;itemenetluse seadustikus (RT I 1993, 49, 693; 2001, 29, 156; 43, 238) s&auml;testatud korras. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) Proceedings in matters concerning administrative offences committed by legal persons provided for in &sect; 30 of this Act, including the imposition and contestation of punishment, shall be conducted pursuant to the procedure established in the Code of Administrative Offences (RT 1992, 29, 396; RT I 1999, 41, 496; 45, correction notice; 58, 608; 60, 616; 87, 792; 92, 825; 95, 843; 2000, 10, 58; 25, 141; 28, 167; 29, 169; 40, 247; 49, 301 and 305; 51, 321; 54, 346, 348 and 351; 55, 361; 58, 376; 84, 533; 86, 544 and 548; 89, 578; 95, 609 and 613; 2001, 3, 5; 17, 76; 18, 87; 21, 115 and 116; 31, 174; 42, 236; 52, 303; 53, 312, 313 and 314; 56, 333, 335 and 339; 58, 356) and the Code of Enforcement Procedure (RT I 1993, 49, 693; 2001, 29, 156; 43, 238). </inglise>
<eesti>(2) K&auml;esoleva seaduse &sect;-s 30 s&auml;testatud haldus&otilde;iguserikkumiste asjade arutamise ja karistuse m&auml;&auml;ramise &otilde;igus on Sideameti peadirektoril ja maa- v&otilde;i linnakohtul. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) The Director General of the Communications Board and county and city courts have the right to hear matters regarding administrative offences provided for in &sect; 30 of this Act and to impose punishments. </inglise>
<eesti>Sideameti peadirektoril on &otilde;igus m&auml;&auml;rata rahatrahv kuni 20 000 krooni ulatuses. </eesti>
<inglise>The Director General of the Communications Board has the right to impose fines of up to 20 000 kroons. </inglise>
