<eesti>Enne k&auml;esoleva seaduse j&otilde;ustumist v&auml;ljastatud ajutised t&auml;htajalised load, kaabeltelevisiooniv&otilde;rgu load ja kaabeltelevisiooniv&otilde;rgu kasutusload </eesti>
<inglise>Temporary licences for a specified term, cable television network licences and cable television network utilisation licences issued before entry into force of this Act </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Enne k&auml;esoleva seaduse j&otilde;ustumist Sideameti poolt v&auml;ljastatud ajutise t&auml;htajalise loa, kaabeltelevisiooniv&otilde;rgu loa v&otilde;i kaabeltelevisiooniv&otilde;rgu kasutusloa alusel v&otilde;ib kaabelleviv&otilde;rgu opereerimist j&auml;tkata kuni kaabelleviv&otilde;rguloa v&auml;ljastamiseni tingimusel, et kolme kuu jooksul k&auml;esoleva seaduse j&otilde;ustumisest arvates esitab nimetatud loa omanik taotluse kaabelleviv&otilde;rguloa v&auml;ljastamiseks. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) The holder of a temporary licence for a specified term, cable television network licence or cable television network utilisation licence which was issued by the Communications Board before the entry into force of this Act may continue to operate a cable network on the basis of such licence until the holder of such licence is granted a cable network licence on condition that the holder of the licence applies for the issue of a cable network licence within three months after the entry into force of this Act. </inglise>
<eesti>Sideamet v&auml;ljastab kaabelleviv&otilde;rguloa hiljemalt kuue kuu jooksul taotluse esitamisest arvates. </eesti>
<inglise>The Communications Board shall issue a cable network licence not later than six months after the date of application. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Kui ajutise t&auml;htajalise loa, kaabeltelevisiooniv&otilde;rgu loa v&otilde;i kaabeltelevisiooniv&otilde;rgu kasutusloa omanik ei esita kolme kuu jooksul k&auml;esoleva seaduse j&otilde;ustumisest arvates taotlust kaabelleviv&otilde;rguloa v&auml;ljastamiseks, kaotab ajutine t&auml;htajaline luba, kaabeltelevisiooniv&otilde;rgu luba v&otilde;i kaabeltelevisiooniv&otilde;rgu kasutusluba kehtivuse k&auml;esoleva seaduse j&otilde;ustumisest kolme kuu m&ouml;&ouml;dumisel. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) If the holder of a temporary licence for a specified term, cable television network licence or cable television network utilisation licence does not apply for the issue of a cable network licence within three months after the entry into force of this Act, the temporary licence for a specified term, cable television network licence or cable television network utilisation licence becomes invalid within three months after the entry into force of this Act. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 34. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 34. </inglise>
<eesti>Enne k&auml;esoleva seaduse j&otilde;ustumist v&auml;ljastatud &uuml;hisantennis&uuml;steemi kasutusload </eesti>
<inglise>Master antenna system utilisation licences issued before entry into force of this Act </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Enne k&auml;esoleva seaduse j&otilde;ustumist v&auml;ljastatud &uuml;hisantennis&uuml;steemi kasutusloa alusel registreerib Sideamet &uuml;hisantennis&uuml;steemi nelja n&auml;dala jooksul, arvates k&auml;esoleva seaduse j&otilde;ustumisest. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) The Communications Board shall register master antenna systems on the basis of the master antenna system utilisation licences issued before entry into force of this Act within four weeks after the entry into force of this Act. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) K&auml;esoleva paragrahvi l&otilde;ikes 1 nimetatud &uuml;hisantennis&uuml;steemi kasutusluba tunnistatakse kehtetuks k&auml;esoleva seaduse &sect; 18 l&otilde;ikes 4 nimetatud k&auml;skkirjaga. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) A master antenna utilisation licence specified in subsection (1) of this section is revoked by a directive specified in subsection 18 (4) of this Act. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 35. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 35. </inglise>
<eesti>Enne k&auml;esoleva seaduse j&otilde;ustumist kohaliku omavalitsuse poolt taotletud kaabeltelevisiooniv&otilde;rgu loa avalikud konkursid </eesti>
<inglise>Public competitions for cable television network licences requested by local governments before entry into force of this Act </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Enne k&auml;esoleva seaduse j&otilde;ustumist kohaliku omavalitsuse poolt taotletud kaabeltelevisiooniv&otilde;rgu loa avalikud konkursid, mis ei ole k&auml;esoleva seaduse j&otilde;ustumise ajaks v&auml;lja kuulutatud, t&uuml;histatakse. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) Public competitions for cable television network licences requested by local governments before the entry into force of this Act which have not been announced by the date of entry into force of this Act shall be revoked. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Enne k&auml;esoleva seaduse j&otilde;ustumist kohaliku omavalitsuse poolt taotletud kaabeltelevisiooniv&otilde;rgu loa avalikud konkursid, mis on k&auml;esoleva seaduse j&otilde;ustumise ajaks v&auml;lja kuulutatud ja ei ole l&otilde;ppenud, t&uuml;histatakse. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) Public competitions for cable television network licences requested by local governments before the entry into force of this Act which have been announced but not terminated by the date of entry into force of this Act shall be revoked. </inglise>
<eesti>T&uuml;histamise teade avaldatakse samades v&auml;ljaannetes, kus konkursi teade. </eesti>
<inglise>The notice concerning the revoking of a competition shall be published in the same publications as the notice by which the competition was announced. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 36. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 36. </inglise>
<eesti>Enne k&auml;esoleva seaduse j&otilde;ustumist tarbijaga s&otilde;lmitud kaabelleviteenuse osutamise lepingud </eesti>
<inglise>Contracts for provision of cable distribution services entered into with consumers before entry into force of this Act </inglise>
<eesti>Enne k&auml;esoleva seaduse j&otilde;ustumist tarbijaga s&otilde;lmitud kaabelleviteenuse osutamise lepingud tuleb viia k&auml;esoleva seaduse n&otilde;uetega vastavusse &uuml;he aasta jooksul, arvates k&auml;esoleva seaduse j&otilde;ustumisest. </eesti>
<inglise>Contracts for provision of cable distribution services entered into with consumers before the entry into force of this Act shall be brought into compliance with the requirements of this Act within one year after the entry into force of this Act. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 37. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 37. </inglise>
